description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 70, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Leverage for East, Nine Lives for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [70 Votes, Common]
